JDE+ a middleware for robotics applications

INSTALL

Configure : ./configure
Compile   : make
Install   : make install
Uninstall : make uninstall

Default instalation path /usr/local[bin|include]. It can be changed 
configuring like this ./configure --prefix=[new-path]. See more options
with ./configure --help.

EXAMPLES

To compile and test examples you must define environment variable
JDE_PATH, with jde+ installation path. Go to examples dir, make to
compile examples. Use "run_hierarchy" script to run each example.
